  "contentHtml": "<div><div><div><div><div><div><p><p>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"line-height: 25pt;\">各有关学院：</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 31.8pt; line-height: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">为充分利用学校学科专业优势，突出办学特色，提高人才培养质量和就业竞争力，经学校本科教学指导委员会同意在<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span>级中医学、针灸推拿学、临床医学等专业开展特色选修模块教学。经过网络报名，现将徐怀等<span lang=\"EN-US\">273</span>位确认修读各模块的同学名单予以公示，公示期：<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">-7</span>日（<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>个工作日），公示期间如有异议，请与教务处联系，联系人：肖老师，联系电话：<span lang=\"EN-US\">22861010</span>。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\r\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 18pt; line-height: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; </span>附：<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span>级特色模块报名公示名单</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-indent: 18pt; line-height: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 18pt; line-height: 18pt; text-align: right;\"><span